  "intent_precise": "0479ad-part-2.ot2.apiv2: Using reagent_plate (labware, slot Reagent Plate at 4 Degrees C), input_plate (labware, slot Fragmented, Primed Poly(A) RNA at 4 Degrees C). With Temperature Module module, Temperature Module module, magnetic module. (1) Wait 10 seconds. (2) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (3) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (4) Disengage magnets to release beads. (5) Pause: format (6) Transfer 10\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (7) Pause: \nRemove the RNA plate for off-deck incubation\n    (25 C 10 min, 42 C 15 min, 70 C 15 min, cool to 4), return and resume\n (8) Wait 1 seconds. (9) Mix 10 times at 64\u00b5L.",
